      "span_text": "This is because, thanks to the repetition code, the entire matrix A, and hence the product (1), can be recovered by combining the information available at the non-straggling servers when we store uncoded rows from matrix A. As compared to the policy in  , a higher storage redundancy r 2 = Kµ = 3 is obtained for the repetition code."
